            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "歐洲天然氣補庫風險上升;摩根士丹利警告TTF可能升至90歐元",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/7vsPtL1T0bhwOtrhhdrpEg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/indicatornews_4_M_1440048337.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"摩根士丹利\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:摩根士丹利;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/摩根士丹利\">摩根士丹利</a>警告稱,在確認卡塔爾拉斯拉凡設施的兩座液化<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"天然氣\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:天然氣;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/天然氣\">天然氣</a>大型生產線遭受長期損壞後,歐洲今夏面臨天然氣儲備補充不足的風險大幅上升。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該行在最新報告中表示,已將「基本情境調整為情境4——預測TTF將在夏季達到90歐元/兆瓦時」,較目前遠期曲線上漲約45%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">分析師Charlotte Firkins表示,此次損壞相當於「未來3年以上全球市場約1300萬噸/年或3%的供應衝擊」,並補充稱該事件已「在一定程度上使天然氣價格與霍爾木茲海峽的局勢脫鉤」。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-3b92a09f-f921-3604-9967-ff4959bb2e17-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">摩根士丹利目前預計2026年全球液化天然氣將出現1500萬噸的缺口。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管歐洲近期基本面仍然寬鬆,但該行表示「夏季儲氣補充的風險已經加劇」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">為確保足夠的天然氣供應,「TTF必須定價以在夏季吸引現貨貨物流向歐洲」,下一個催化劑將是「進入夏季後現貨市場緊張程度上升」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">摩根士丹利提到可能出現「6月/7月搶購液化天然氣貨物的熱潮」,警告稱爭奪供應可能將TTF推高至90歐元/兆瓦時。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該行還指出,歐洲各國政府可能需要「再次補貼儲氣容量預訂以鼓勵儲氣補充」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該行補充稱,如果拉斯拉凡停產延續至6月或更長時間,價格可能重回「2022年式的100-200歐元/兆瓦時或更高水平」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">摩根士丹利還將其2027年預測上調至約45歐元/兆瓦時,理由是卡塔爾產量損失和卡塔爾擴建項目延遲導致長期緊張狀況。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2%E5%A4%A9%E7%84%B6%E6%B0%A3%E8%A3%9C%E5%BA%AB%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%87-%E6%91%A9%E6%A0%B9%E5%A3%AB%E4%B8%B9%E5%88%A9%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8Attf%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E5%8D%87%E8%87%B390%E6%AD%90%E5%85%83-143352922.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-20 23:01:21",
